snippet.title: Johnny Depp ATTACKED By Amber Heard Fan During Red Carpet Interview
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp ATTACKED By Amber Heard Fan During Red Carpet Interview


Hi and welcome back to Hot Talk, where you can get the latest updates in Hollywood! After the messy breakup and legal battle between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard, things have not been looking too bright for either of them in the spotlight. Amidst Depp's personal life, he hit the red carpet at the Deauville Film Festival where he got attacked by an Amber Heard fan during an interview. To know the whole story, watch the full video here. 


Subscribe to Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCklWVtkuo5FYPNLNqQTdiNQ


Thank you for watching and if you enjoyed our content please don’t forget to leave a like, comment, and subscribe to our channel.
